1ec0U TRUY\u1ec0N TH\u1ed0NG<\/h1><div class=\"ffb-id-4u1l4i1h fg-paragraph ff-richtext text-center text-sm-center text-md-center text-lg-center fg-text-dark\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Th&aacute;ng 9 n&agrave;y, th\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee9c ti\u1ec7c tr&agrave; Heritage High Tea sang tr\u1ecdng trong b\u1ea7u kh&ocirc;ng kh&iacute; \u1ea5m &aacute;p v\u1edbi t\u1ea7m nh&igrave;n tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1eb9p h\u01b0\u1edbng ra th&agrave;nh ph\u1ed1 t\u1ea1i Cafe de l'Opera.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1eafm ch&igrave;m trong b\u1eefa ti\u1ec7c tr&agrave; chi\u1ec1u tinh t\u1ebf v&agrave; thanh l\u1ecbch v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a c&aacute;c lo\u1ea1i b&aacute;nh tuy\u1ec7t h\u1ea3o c&ugrave;ng v\u1edbi tr&agrave; v&agrave; c&agrave; ph&ecirc;. S\u1ebd tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi h\u01a1n n\u1eefa khi ti\u1ec7c tr&agrave; chi\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi r\u01b0\u1ee3u vang h\u1ed3ng v&agrave; vang s\u1ee7i th\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u1ea1ng.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">* VND 590,000++, g\u1ed3m m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n tr&agrave; ho\u1eb7c c&agrave; ph&ecirc;<br \/>* VND 890,000++, g\u1ed3m m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n Jagerbomb<br \/>* VND 1,090,000++, g\u1ed3m m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n tr&agrave; ho\u1eb7c c&agrave; ph&ecirc; v&agrave; m\u1ed9t ly r\u01b0\u1ee3u vang s\u1ee7i<\/p>\n<p><\/div><div class=\"ffb-id-5ggirhco buttons-el-wrapper text-center    fg-text-dark\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/datashre\/heritage-hightea-menu.pdf\" class=\"ffb-block-button-1-0 ffb-btn ffb-btn-v1 ffb-btn-link  btn-base-brd-slide btn-slide  btn-base-md    btn-w-auto fg-text-dark ffb-button1-1\"><span class=\"btn-text\">TH\u1ef0C \u0110\u01a0N<\/span><\/a><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/section><style>.ffb-id-4u1l4i19{ padding-top: 50px;padding-right: 50px;padding-bottom: 50px;padding-left: 50px;} .ffb-id-4u1l4i1a{ text-align: center;}.ffb-id-5ggirhco .ffb-button1-1.ffb-block-button-1-0